The defence in the Senzo Meyiwa trial says the High court in Pretoria has no jurisdiction to hear the matter. Malesela Teffo, who represents four of the accused, claims his clients' rights are being violated. Meanwhile, some are accusing him of trying to delay the case. Legal expert Mpume Zikalala discussed this with eNCA's Masego Rahlaga. Courtesy of #DStv403